title: My profile prioritizing Flex over Solo/Que?
body: When I go into customs it shows my rank as Bronze 1 even though I am Gold 3 in Soloque. Is there a reason why it's prioritizing Flex over Soloque?

replies.body:
I was able to reproduce this as well, so it looks like it may be intended. If you'd like to leave feedback on this, I recommend posting in the [**Client Discussion Boards.**](http://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/alpha-client-discussion)

If you have any other questions, let me know.
